name: Globally inspired patterns :-)
description:
I was previously designing in SF, and I've quit my job to travel around the world for a year, hoping to learn more about different cultures so that it would make me a more informed human being + designer :-) 

Through traveling, I hope to understand how history has influenced art genres, and will be translating my findings into globally inspired patterns!

Follow me on my journey on Twitter @jchangsta :-)
